## 2026-04-08 — Session 1

**Tasks completed:** T001, T002, T003, T004, T005, T006 (partial), T010, T016

**Summary:**
Bootstrapped the entire EmpireOS project from scratch. No prior game/ directory existed.

**Files created:**
- `game/CLAUDE.md` — coding standards and architecture guide
- `game/.intel/roadmap.md` — 6-phase roadmap (T001–T024)
- `game/.intel/tasks.json` — full task backlog with priorities
- `game/.intel/execution.log` — this log
- `game/index.html` — entry point with HUD, tab bar, content panels
